{"tid":1639047,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［柒到台灣］香港上海商銀被誤認為陸資遭攻擊 確認營運正常無虞","createTime":"2019-10-08T13:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T23:22:50.000Z","uid":158766,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"44d7f1ed5cdae3fe1b178644a8a81057d419fcf6","tid":1639047,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:32:05.000Z","msg":"香港反送中風波持續延燒，香港政府《禁蒙面法》生效後，傳出台資的上海商業儲蓄銀行，因被誤認為陸資遭攻擊，連帶使得在香港的台資銀行營運狀況備受關切，金管會今 (8) 日表示，據上海商銀回報，營運一切正常；至於金融業曝險金額連 2 個月在兆元以下。<br />\n<br />\n《禁蒙面法》10 月 5 日生效後，香港局勢日益惡化，示威者怒砸陸資店舖，其中被攻擊包括台資的上海商業儲蓄銀行，也因為被誤認為陸資，遭潑漆攻擊，所幸事後有香港網友澄清上海商銀是台資銀行，紛紛發文道歉才化解攻擊風波。<br />\n<br />\n對於上海商銀被誤認為陸資遭攻擊一事，金管會表示，根據該行回報，僅被示威者噴漆，隔天就正常營業，並未停業，ATM 也非網路上傳言已毀，而只是被噴漆而已，也沒有分行出現停業狀況，上海商銀在香港據點目前營運一切正常，。<br />\n<br />\n其他國銀在香港，是否營運有受到波及？金管會指出，由於國銀在香港分行或子行，多是以企業金融為主要客戶，而非一般消費者，加上放款也都是參與聯貸案，因此，就目前為止，尚未發現有明顯的衝擊。金管會將持續密切關注香港最新政經情勢動向與發展，也提醒國銀要事先做好因應準備及風險控管。<br />\n<br />\n至於金融業對香港曝險金額，據金管會統計，6 月底時為 1 兆 282 億元，但 7 月底降至 9934.96 億元，8 月底雖小幅增加 10.89 億元，不過僅達 9945.85 億元，等於連續 2 個月在兆元以下。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4393319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4393319&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VkzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=952f6e88\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4393319</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是其是，非其非！而家比人發現左我地認錯左係陸資，雖然佢地已經收到大家嘅道歉，但文宣組和理非都要加緊手一齊補鑊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">和中有勇，勇中有和，決不割蓆！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZ7SG2N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZ7SG2N.jpg&h=9c175a01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XwO6Mut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwO6Mut.jpg&h=fd292791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9rzUVnN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9rzUVnN.jpg&h=51bea2f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GwOOfnN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGwOOfnN.jpg&h=c545a843&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9220491be3110ec67ec207602ed76b3ec86301e4","tid":1639047,"uid":140924,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"我地道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住 建議改下名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8f06d98677cc663974d370cdc9313ddbab078c","tid":1639047,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:36:00.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"dfd1c8297a61c284f503e90f6f055bc51509703d","tid":1639047,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46d311d6d7d3c7433c9fa7b24c1d07ba9cb76cb1","tid":1639047,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9220491be3110ec67ec207602ed76b3ec86301e4","tid":1639047,"uid":140924,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"我地道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住 建議改下名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /